{
  "stem": "20848.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, [GERMAN] was a roll call, which was in the morning at 5 o'clock they used to take you out of the barrack outside and give you a bit of black water, hot water to drink, what they called coffee.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they used to keep you there for two, three hours to count you.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But the-- the idea was to-- to exhaust you, to stand there for two, three hours so that you will be completely exhausted before the day started.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when you came back, they did the same.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And at the end of the day, they gave you a bit of soup.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But you also stayed there for few hours.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I was just about to come to that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was again talking to the people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And one woman said to me, obviously you have a bit of a luck, and you-- obviously you have a bit of a connections in the camp, she said.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because you don't go to [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This-- somebody is helping you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Why don't you ask to get a job?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It would be very good for you to get a job.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I-- I think that those women, really-- why would they tell me a thing like that?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was all meant to be-- I really-- I'm a believer, you know?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I-- I read somewhere that when you witness terrible atrocities in life, terrible cruelty, you either turn away from God altogether or you become a believe.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Do you know that?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I think that's what happened to me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I went again to this Mr-- to this Kaminski, Chaim Kaminski, who said to me that after the war, if we survive, he's going to adopt me and we'll go and live in Palestine.",
      "word_count": 35
    }
  ],
